{"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/10WorkflowUI6ScreenP","doc:\/\/WorkflowModals\/10WorkflowUI22SingleScreenContainingP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModalContainer","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"BaseContent","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModalContent","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When modals are added or removed from a container, the screen will animate the changes based on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the modals keys. If new modals are added, a presentation animation will occur, and if modals are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"removed, a dismissal animation will occur. Existing modals will have their screens updated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This container uses the modal system to trampoline modals to a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHost"},{"type":"text","text":", which must be installed somewhere in your hierarchy."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In a pure workflow application, you should install a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHostContainer"},{"type":"text","text":" at the root of your app."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In a hybrid application, you should install a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"x-source-tag:\/\/ModalHostContainerViewController"},{"type":